{"tid":317172,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"睇掌我就唔識喇，不過識睇樣。","createTime":"2017-07-11T09:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-10T12:53:00.000Z","uid":7848,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ae6dcf580680905a87e17a862ab7b630e7ca7e7","tid":317172,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"正所謂憨鳩仔有樣睇，隔離po影自己手俾人睇嘅真係十足十個啲無乜點讀過書嘅師奶仔。<br />\n<br />\n影兩張相，影下手仔就知自己有無錢嘅話，的確係幾犀利嘅。不過人地睇完同你講，你會發達，唔通又真係坐係度就會有錢跌落嚟俾你咩?<br />\n<br />\n打少陣飛機，發少陣夢啦傻仔。睇掌睇到會唔會發達，三歲細路哥都會問點解啦。<br />\n<br />\n見到成班憨鳩走去問，會唔會發達，發夢就有你份。真係人唔笑狗都吠啦，同個啲日日都追tvb劇嘅師奶有咩分別，唔怪得之香港咁耐都無乜點進步，成班後生嘅都唔識用腦諗野。<br />\n<br />\n喂唔爭在幫我睇埋會唔會發達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/171136_b49bc59ea00e24ea309293b86ebdc3f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F171136_b49bc59ea00e24ea309293b86ebdc3f4.jpg&h=3fb63da4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8af8f5e43dab88a5c8a9d6439d822c13fc8c4843","tid":317172,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:13:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c8a5873cf7104ed15401f2be735539a75fea5f","tid":317172,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"睇掌佬俾我講中咗就負評啊?"},{"pid":"3d193d12a209e8cfdaf84587886cae8e6055a46d","tid":317172,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:16:23.000Z","msg":"關你舉中指咩事？"},{"pid":"e27bcb2247e11a6dab5f9774bd2fcb613c316b8e","tid":317172,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>關你舉中指咩事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌真係好撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a578a637a49cbfaaea4d3edf5f00c70401296c02","tid":317172,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":2,"